{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2524175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可不可以这么考虑：甲乙都99，平局甲赢。甲获胜概率多出来的那部分就是平局出现的概率。这时乙多出一个硬币，以二分之一的概率逆转结果，所以分走了原先甲多出来的获胜概率的一半。所以一样大。", "timestamp": 1631805131, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524250, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我不知道算得对不对，但是一个个算下来是一样大", "timestamp": 1631805578, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "洞主公布答案吧！", "timestamp": 1631805586, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524255, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 每期答案大约在发下一期的时候公布嘛。", "timestamp": 1631805632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524288, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524266, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好呀，但是我觉得上期好难，上期dz啥时候发", "timestamp": 1631805715, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524301, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524175, "tag": null, "text": "或者考虑所有可能情况，一共是100*101个点。甲多了y=x这条线上的100个点，乙多了x=100这条线上的100个点，所以一样多。", "timestamp": 1631805769, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524288, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 确实上期相当难（也相当长）。上期的答案是 2 ，但是证明可能等上期 B 君发出来吧……", "timestamp": 1631805872, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524301, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这些点不是等可能的吧。", "timestamp": 1631805888, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524366, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": 2524331, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哦确实，傻了傻了", "timestamp": 1631806040, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524421, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2338, "w": 3648}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1631806302, "type": "image", "url": "cm/cmbfg6gqoou46nsv6547yjteqyjbz7my.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2524428, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这期是这样吗？我不知道是不是我想简单了", "timestamp": 1631806317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524452, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊左下的49写成48了，但是结果不影响", "timestamp": 1631806390, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2525412, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "让乙先抛 99 枚，这时若正面个数甲 > 乙则甲必然获胜，乙 > 甲则乙必然获胜，这两种情况等可能；甲 = 乙时，乙再抛一次硬币，则甲乙获胜还是等可能。于是综合考虑，两人获胜概率相同。", "timestamp": 1631810348, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2556298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482100, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "答案：一样大。一个合理的解释是，先一人抛 99 个。如果不是平局，则乙再抛一个也无济于事，所以直接判定胜负，在此阶段双方是公平的；如果平局则进行加时赛，乙抛一个硬币决定胜负。", "timestamp": 1632152152, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 482100, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "#每晚问题 26 #数洞计划～\n上期 #480767\n今甲和乙玩抛硬币游戏，规则如下：甲抛掷 99 枚硬币，乙抛掷 100 枚硬币，出现正面个数多的获胜。平局的情况，算甲获胜。\n问题是，谁获胜的概率大？", "timestamp": 1631804699, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632152149, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"甲": 9, "乙": 5, "一样大": 30, "瓜": 15}, "vote_options": ["甲", "乙", "一样大", "瓜"]}}}